h4. Steps to Reproduce (tested with a local JIRA 6.3.13 and JSD 2.1.1):
# Add a google mail as the outgoing mail server;
# Create a project/service desk;
# Create an issue as a customer;
# As an agent, attach an image to the issue;
# Add a comment to the issue:
{noformat:borderStyle=dashed| borderColor=#6A8EB3 |bgColor=#F8F8F8}
!^my-attachment.png!
{noformat}

h4. Expected Behavior:
The email notification would show the attached image for the JSD notifications.

h4. Actual Results:
The notification does not display the image attached inline with the notifications on JSD.
!Screen Shot 2015-01-16 at 7.43.20 PM.png!

h4. Workaround:

Use the markup !https://jira.atlassian.com/secure/attachment/148304/code.png! to present the image rather than showing it as an inline attachment.

