Whenever the 'Pause' and 'Stop' conditions are the same, the SLA would not work properly (see JSD-1249).

It would be very helpful if there could be a message in JIRA to notify the user that the two conditions are the same, and not allow them to save that kind of configuration. This would avoid any potential confusion and problems that might arise from that behavior.

